title: Think Before You Act  ( Earth Gang Interview)
itunes:title: Think Before You Act  ( Earth Gang Interview)
description:
Today we had the duo Earth Gang, who are first timers to come stop by on the show! They spoke about Atlanta collectively, Spillage Village and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day to an American Tourist who faked abduction to get out of quarantine in Jamaica and we opened up the phone lines to see if our listeners thought Meek Mill should have done when Tekashi pulled up on him over the weekend.
